<b>Announcement:</b> GnuCash 2.6.15 Release
2016-12-18

<h2>GnuCash 2.6.15 released</h2>

<p>The GnuCash development team announces GnuCash 2.6.15, the fifteenth maintenance release in the 2.6-stable series.
